Deck exists - reorganize
--------------------------------
1. extract apkg
2. reorganize media - images and sound - use rename.sh (edit fileExtension at file, before executing)
3. move edited media into anki collection.media folder - /home/xxx/.local/share/Anki2/userxyz/collection.media/-
4. use template.ods and edit
5. save edited template as .csv with comma seperation plus UTF-8 format
6. import csv and activate allow HTML in fields plus order field mapping

-----------------------------------

New Deck

1. use template.ods fill in column name plus fields
2. organize your media into one media folder and seperate it to image folder and sound folder - images and sound - if needed use rename.sh
3. move edited media into anki collection.media folder - /home/xxx/.local/share/Anki2/userxyz/collection.media/-
4. save edited template as .csv with comma seperation plus UTF-8 format
5. import csv and activate allow HTML in fields plus order field mapping
-----------------------------------


